	(text_box "This merger board seeks to combine the SCALES EPS board with the SCALES IMX8 Carrier Board. Both boards have undergone three revisions, this merger will combine the final revisions of both with each of them undergoing some more modifications based on seperate board reviews.\nNotable differences for each board compared to their individual counterparts are listed below.\n\nEPS: Based on the Rev F Schematic / Viking 1-C model, (Modificaitions based on suggestions by A. Greenberg)\n- Watchdog removed for Peripheral Board\n- More decoupling capacitors for inrush current mitigation for Jetson bootup sequence\n- Resistors to bias EN lines for the perif/jetson\n- Resistors to current limit Watchdog outputs\n\nIMX8X Carrier Board: Based on the Mariner 1-C board (Modifications suggested by Phytec)\n- \n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 13.208 22.86 0)
		(size 106.172 60.452)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
